    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a torque-sensing variable M differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and recent valve clearance adjustment. The chassis is reinforced at the rear subframe mounting points and features refreshed poly-bushes for sharpened lateral dynamics. A true driver\u2019s spec with robust mechanical provenance and linear power delivery.",
