    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it has been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-cared for, making it the perfect choice if you're looking for something dependable and clean without the 'brand new' price tag. It runs beautifully and is totally ready for its next adventure\u2014I'm sure you're going to love it as much as I have!",
      "price": 33800.0,
