    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system. This driver-spec example features the sought-after Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-calibrated limited-slip differential. The chassis has been enhanced with rear subframe reinforcement to address common platform fatigue, maintaining structural integrity under high lateral loads. Recent service includes a cooling system refresh and valve adjustment to ensure the powerplant operates within peak thermal and mechanical tolerances. The suspension remains tight, utilizing its original MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear geometry for precise turn-in. An honest, performance-oriented machine for the purist.",
